items.checkin_comment: Hits of grapefruit, pine and syrupy malt. It feels quite dialed back for the masses, but ultimately makes for a more sessionable West Coast adjacent IPA. Flavours build with time and do start packing a punch, but evolution is drowned by the bitterness.
